<item>
            <title>[LU-15930] Remove duplicate checks for peer sensitivity</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15930</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Callers of lnet_inc_lpni_healthv_locked() and&lt;br/&gt;
lnet_dec_healthv_locked() currently check whether the parent peer&lt;br/&gt;
has a peer specific sensitivity defined. This duplication should be removed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can also modify lnet_dec_healthv_locked() to return a bool indicating&lt;br/&gt;
whether the health value was actually modified so that the peer&lt;br/&gt;
net health is only updated when the peer NI health actually changes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
